Dalgety shares tumble after profit warning . Shares in Dalgety Plc dropped in pre - market trading on Wednesday after the food and agribusineess company warned that results in the second half would fall short of its performance in the first half of the year . The stock was down 48p at 262 - 1 / 2 by 0710 GMT in volume of 60 , 000 shares . The company also said it would cut its dividend , with a total payout this year expected to be not less than 14 . 5p compared with 22p a year before . It said third - quarter profits for petfoods and agriculture had been disappointing and the strength of sterling had continued to affect profits . - - David Holmes , London Newsroom + 44 171 542 4367 
